This paper discusses collaborative machine learning markets, which involves the intersection of machine learning (cs.LG), game theory (cs.GT), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses potential threats, including data replication, which falls under the category of computer security and cryptography (cs.CR). Additionally, the paper introduces a novel payment division function, which involves algorithms and data structures (cs.DS).
